Reasoning: 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely category as the paper discusses attacks on the encryption scheme of the Moscow Internet Voting System.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of technology in the voting system and its impact on society.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper discusses the development and testing of the Internet voting system.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of ElGamal encryption, which is a cryptographic algorithm.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a possible category as the paper discusses the security of the Internet voting system and the vulnerabilities in its encryption scheme.
